{"tid":2382554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年被指淋液體　六旬婦認不出被告　片段看不清容貌　辯方質疑：憑咩推論？","createTime":"2021-01-27T10:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T12:52:41.000Z","uid":56115,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"41759481e88f7295f1460c1d902a17ceff6f3111","tid":2382554,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"網民去年 5 月 6 日在天水圍發起「和你唱」，期間一名 69 歲婦人被指拍攝在場人士，遭數名男子襲擊。<span class=\"red\">15 歲少年被指向婦人淋液體，否認襲擊致造成身體傷害罪</span>，今（27 日）在屯門裁判法院受審。本案無傳召事主及警員出庭作供，僅播放新聞片段及閉路片段。辯方指呈堂片段未能辨認涉案人容貌，「所有識別資料都冇特殊地方」，質疑未能推論片中男子是被告。案件押至 2 月 18 日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑警方在案發 6 日後搜屋，該批衫褲亦無沒有特別識別之處，「冇象徵意義，唔代表啲咩」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">事主在口供亦沒有提及穿綠色衫的人襲擊她</span>。辯方質疑僅憑新聞片段，未能推論綠衫男子為被告，更指「（新聞片段）直頭唔應該呈堂」。"},{"pid":"e8f0a8a47ee22899ce8f0ae158e30cdc60c2a4d7","tid":2382554,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-6-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D-%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%B7%8B%E6%B6%B2%E9%AB%94-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%B2%8C-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%86%91%E5%92%A9%E6%8E%A8%E8%AB%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-6-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B7%258B%25E6%25B6%25B2%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25B2%258C-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591-%25E6%2586%2591%25E5%2592%25A9%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25AB%2596%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=915c407b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-6-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B7%258B%25E6%25B6%25B2%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25B2%258C-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591-%25E6%2586%2591%25E5%2592%25A9%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25AB%2596%2F&h=bdc04355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-6-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D-%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%B7%8B%E6%B6%B2%E9%AB%94-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%B2%8C-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%86%91%E5%92%A9%E6%8E%A8%E8%AB%96/</a>"},{"pid":"d70592e9b33ee3bea705edacaf08bb512a7b69e7","tid":2382554,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b8901f87f0ba52c4b731c376f3272b29a23255","tid":2382554,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"控方今<span class=\"red\">僅於庭上播放多段閉路電視片段作證</span>，沒有傳召任何證人作供。辯方大律師郭憬憲陳詞指，案中沒有任何人能證明片中人是被告，重申「相似係唔夠嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官<span class=\"red\">王證瑜</span>下令案件押後至下月18日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n15歲男學生面對一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，指他於去年5月6日非法襲擊女子<span class=\"red\">陳粵華</span>（69歲）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/E66XMNBYCJBD3MQ5QZNYPZMK2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FE66XMNBYCJBD3MQ5QZNYPZMK2I%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=dbfa4174\" data-e